{"tid":2062041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：公務員是透過偽政權間接向共產黨負責 仍須偽裝一國兩制出力","createTime":"2020-06-13T00:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T00:47:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f07a5184d58f52f92bf13452c0191c065e7c53","tid":2062041,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"聶德權：公務員是透過行政長官向中央負責<br />\n13.06.2020 08:32<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權早前表示，特區政府公務員同時是國家的公務員，執行職務時要考慮兩重身分。他在本台節目再次就言論解話，指公務員是向特區政府及行政長官負責，而行政長官透過中央任命，所以公務員是透過行政長官向中央負責。他又指，香港是一國之下的特別行政區，回歸後已納入國家治理體系，而本港實行一國兩制，制度與內地不同，包括公務員制度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1307913&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1307913%26csid%3D261_341&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=9388427c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1307913&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"bdcb1a044b786bd53cee6b8b439049ab13c9abd9","tid":2062041,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e683dfc2444308296cba92826bb830bc887fc2c","tid":2062041,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"你老母份糧邊撚個出俾你"},{"pid":"384ee0dc90d7392b3731c4466f2164f9c0602181","tid":2062041,"uid":321803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:46:08.000Z","msg":"中國人無份納香港稅收<br />\n點解香港要無條件照顧埋中國人?"},{"pid":"aff04fa004c256d14e6bf610eeeac35bd6109e10","tid":2062041,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk-appledaily-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M9FUO0vn8XH8_fZrmgF4VusaCbg=/d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/06-11-2020/t_e077458112a74cff